# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# SMSHIVE — Environment Variables
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── Database ──────────────────────────────
MONGODB_URI=mongodb://localhost:27017/smshive
# For Docker: mongodb://mongo:27017/smshive
# For Atlas:  mongodb+srv://user:pass@cluster.mongodb.net/smshive

# ── JWT Authentication ────────────────────
JWT_SECRET=your-super-secret-jwt-key-change-this
JWT_EXPIRATION=7d
JWT_REFRESH_SECRET=your-refresh-secret-change-this
JWT_REFRESH_EXPIRATION=30d

# ── Google OAuth (Optional) ──────────────
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=

# ── Backend Server ────────────────────────
API_PORT=8000
API_URL=http://localhost:8000
CORS_ORIGINS=http://localhost:3000

# ── Frontend ──────────────────────────────
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:8000
NEXT_PUBLIC_WS_URL=http://localhost:8000
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_NAME=SMSHIVE
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=http://localhost:3000

# ── Email (Nodemailer SMTP) ──────────────
SMTP_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
SMTP_PORT=587
SMTP_USER=
SMTP_PASS=
SMTP_FROM=noreply@smshive.app

# ── Redis (Optional — for queuing) ───────
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379
# For Docker: redis://redis:6379

# ── Docker MongoDB ────────────────────────
MONGO_USER=smshive
MONGO_PASSWORD=smshive_secret_change_this
